<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(4000, '2006-12-12', NULL, '<div class=\"details\" id=\"December 12, 2006\" style=\"display: none;\">
Changes/Additions
	<ul>
<li> Disabled player drowning</li> <li> Can now modify the \'strength\' of hoverballs</li> <li> CS Weapon changes</li> <li> Added emitter STOOL</li> </ul>
Bug fixes
	<ul>
<li> Dedicated Servers not mounting mods/addons</li> <li> [Fixed] \"Joining Server\" console spam when joining a server</li> <li> [Fixed] Antlion Guard crashes</li> <li> [Fixed] Weapons sometimes appearing not to fire in multiplayer</li> <li> [Fixed] Lamps not being added to Cleanup</li> <li> [Fixed] Lamp spawning crash</li> <li> [Fixed] Vehicles menu not being filled when loading a save</li> <li> [Fixed] Not being able to change hoverball settings after creation</li> <li> [Fixed] Max 255 ConVar crash after installing mods</li> <li> [Fixed] Draworder oddities with dynamite, thrusters etc</li> </ul>
</div>'),
(4000, '2006-12-12', 'Garry\'s Mod Update Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_875\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Updates to Garry\'s Mod have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Garry\'s Mod</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Disabled player drowning<br/><li>Can now modify the \'strength\' of hoverballs<br/><li>Fixed Dedicated Servers not mounting mods/addons<br/><li>Fixed \"Joining Server\" console spam when joining a server<br/><li>Fixed Antlion Guard crashes<br/><li>Fixed weapons sometimes appearing not to fire in multiplayer <br/><li>Fixed lamps not being added to Cleanup<br/><li>Fixed lamp spawning crash <br/><li>Fixed vehicles menu not being filled when loading a save<br/><li>Fixed not being able to change hoverball settings after creation<br/><li>Fixed max 255 ConVar crash after installing mods<br/><li>Fixed draworder oddities with dynamite, thrusters etc</li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(4000, '2006-12-20', NULL, '<div class=\"details\" id=\"December 20, 2006\" style=\"display: none;\">
Changes/Additions
	<ul>
<li> [Added] Prop Spawner toolmode</li> <li> [Added] Turret toolmode</li> <li> [Added] Clicking an existing balloon now updates its colour &amp; material as well as power</li> <li> [Added] Clicking an existing thruster now updates its effect, toggle mode &amp; damage mode, as well as power</li> <li> [Added] Clicking an existing dynamite now updates its power</li> <li> [Added] Clicking an existing lamp now updates its colour</li> <li> [Added] Pressing reload with any constraint toolmode removes all that type of constraint from the targeted prop (includes nocollide &amp; keepupright)</li> <li> [Added] Pressing reload with the remover toolmode removes all constraints from the targeted prop</li> <li> [Added] More useful error messages when client.dll Init() fails</li> <li> [Change] Duplicate welds are now ignored</li> <li> [Change] Welds automatically nocollide the two welded objects together</li> <li> [Change] map2 can now only be called by the server admin (doh)</li> <li> [Change] The undo system is now accurate</li> <li> [Change] Colour change alpha should now always work, regardless of rendermode</li> <li> [Change] Improved stability of constrained objects held by the physgun</li> </ul>
Bug fixes
	<ul>
<li> [Fixed] Undo performance issues</li> <li> [Fixed] Crash when throwing spear at rollermine</li> <li> [Fixed] Max balloon limit reached when attempting to change an existing balloons properties</li> <li> [Fixed] Max emitter limit reached when attempting to change an existing emitters properties</li> <li> [Fixed] Max hoverball limit reached when attempting to change an existing hoverballs properties</li> <li> [Fixed] Hoverball strength not getting set</li> <li> [Fixed] Nailgun nails actually get duplicated properly</li> <li> [Fixed] Rare physgun crash</li> <li> [Fixed] PlayerConnect Event crash</li> <li> [Fixed] Barnacle tongue crash</li> <li> [Fixed] Rare Control Panel crash (on exit)</li> <li> [Fixed] Spawn menu save button not saving, and instead deleting all of your spawn menus</li> <li> [Fixed] Buffer Overrun with 200+ constraints in a constraintsystem</li> <li> [Fixed] Toolgun prediction getting confused about which stage it\'s on</li> <li> [Fixed] Errors when datafolder convar was wrongly defined</li> <li> [Fixed] Wrong tool information being shown if you change tools half way through an action</li> <li> [Fixed] Limit errors when duplicating vehicles</li> <li> [Lua] SWEP:Reload is now called even if the weapon doesn\'t use clips</li> <li> [Lua] ENT:GetSkin now works as intended</li> <li> [Lua] Added GAMEMODE:EntityRemoved( ent )</li> <li> [Lua] Added ENT:CallOnRemove( name, func, args )</li> <li> [Lua] Timers are now pcall\'d</li> <li> [Lua] Fixed crashing when panel callback functions errored</li> <li> [Lua] HUD_PRINTTALK now shows up in single player</li> <li> [Lua] When running a script the global SCRIPTNAME contains the script\'s filename</li> <li> [Lua] Downloaded autoruns should now autorun</li> <li> [Lua] Added util.CRC( <string> )</string></li> </ul>
</div>'),
(4000, '2006-12-20', 'Garry\'s Mod Update Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_884\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Updates to Garry\'s Mod have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Garry\'s Mod</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Added Prop Spawner toolmode<br/><li>Added Turret toolmode<br/><li>Clicking an existing balloon now updates its colour &amp; material as well as power<br/><li>Clicking an existing thruster now updates its effect, toggle mode &amp; damage mode, as well as power <br/><li>Clicking an existing dynamite now updates its power<br/><li>Clicking an existing lamp now updates its colour</li></li></li></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(4000, '2007-01-08', NULL, '<div class=\"details\" id=\"January 8, 2007\" style=\"display: none;\">
Changes/Additions
	<ul>
<li> Added Weld / Easy-weld nocollide until break checkbox</li> <li> Added Spawnmenu search</li> <li> Duplicate nocollides are ignored</li> <li> Sped up download process</li> <li> Deathnotices now use hud_deathnotice_time</li> </ul>
Bug fixes
	<ul>
<li> Fixed turrets Limit error when adjusting existing turret properties in multiplayer</li> <li> Fixed turrets angle not being set when duplicated</li> <li> Fixed elastic constraints always being created as \"Stretch only\"</li> <li> Fixed dynamite not duplicating properly</li> <li> Fixed wrong/Missing text for undo, cleanup and limits</li> <li> Fixed prop spawner spawned props not adding to cleanup</li> <li> Fixed non existent welds getting stuck in the undo menu</li> <li> Fixed client crash when easy welding brush based props</li> <li> Fixed Servername spilling out of scoreboard</li> <li> Manhacks corpses are now clientside</li> <li> Fixed Manhack bleeding</li> <li> Fixed error when unfreezing statues</li> <li> Fixed final click with easy weld sometimes not working</li> <li> Fixed magnetizing props that have been coloured</li> <li> Fixed hoverballs not duplicating properly</li> <li> Fixed reloading with the toolgun calling continuously instead of once when pressed</li> <li> Fixed some model crashes</li> </ul>
</div>'),
(4000, '2007-01-08', 'Garry\'s Mod Update Released', '<div class=\"post_content\" id=\"content_896\" style=\"display: none;\">
<p>Updates to Garry\'s Mod have been released. The updates will be applied automatically when your Steam client is restarted. The specific changes include:<br/><br/><b>Garry\'s Mod</b><br/><ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><li>Added Weld / Easy-weld nocollide until break checkbox<br/><li>Added Spawnmenu search<br/><li>Duplicate nocollides are ignored<br/><li>Sped up download process</li></li></li></li></ul></p>
<br clear=\"left\"/>
</div>'),
(4000, '2007-01-18', NULL, '<div class=\"details\" id=\"January 18, 2007\" style=\"display: block;\">
Changes/Additions
	<ul>
<li> Added New score board</li> <li> Resource adding now works without touching the .res file</li> <li> Tweaked hydraulics/muscle to be less springy</li> <li> Ragdolls no longer stretch</li> <li> Player now presses fire/jump to respawn instead of automatically respawning</li> <li> Added option to disable thruster sound</li> <li> Download system speedups</li> </ul>
Bug fixes
	<ul>
<li> Fixed SENTs/SWEPs sometimes appearing as the wrong class with higher pings</li> <li> Fixed VGUI/Lua crashes</li> <li> Fixed SuperDoF effect being \'wrong\'</li> <li> Fixed rare Lua crash</li> <li> Fixed muscle crash</li> <li> Fixed being able to \'use\' Alyx\'s Gun</li> <li> Fixed Lua Panels getting nuked when reloading a SWEP/SENT</li> <li> Fixed sv_defaultgamemode sometimes causing problems</li> <li> Fixed player vs player damage not working in server creation</li> <li> Fixed really long pause before joining MP games</li> <li> Fixed bot names not being completely set on the sever</li> <li> Fixed NPC gunfire effects now show up properly</li> <li> Fixed player sometimes respawning immediately after being killed</li> </ul>
</div>'),
